gov.nasa.jpf.jvm

Interface ClassFileReader

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClassFileParser, ClassFilePrinter, ClassFileReaderAdapter, JVMAnnotationParser

    public interface ClassFileReader
    interface for classfile processors NOTE - all types are given ss descriptors, i.e. "Lx/y/Z;" or type codes such as "I" iteration groups always start with a setXCount(int xCount) followed by xCount notifications setX (int xIndex) with 0<=xIndex
